pda.view

Class ChoosePhotoView

  • java.lang.Object
    • pda.view.ChoosePhotoView

  • public class ChoosePhotoView
extends java.lang.Object
    The ChoosePhotoView is the page displaying the images of the chosen directory
    It displays thoses images in 2 or 3 columns
    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
    Florent Catiau-Tristant and Mehdi Haddad
